

{"id":5224,"date":"2023-08-07T09:12:46","date_gmt":"2023-08-07T02:12:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=5224"},"modified":"2023-08-07T09:12:46","modified_gmt":"2023-08-07T02:12:46","slug":"ke-hoach-tap-luyen-giam-can-trong-vong-6-tuan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/en\/ke-hoach-tap-luyen-giam-can-trong-vong-6-tuan\/","title":{"rendered":"K\u1ebe HO\u1ea0CH T\u1eacP LUY\u1ec6N GI\u1ea2M C\u00c2N TRONG V\u00d2NG 6 TU\u1ea6N"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n: B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m bao nhi\u00eau c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n, K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n.<\/em><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00f3i quen t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1c nhau &#8211; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m bao nhi\u00eau c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4787\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4787\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4787 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4787\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m bao nhi\u00eau c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n. S\u1ed1 c\u00e2n an to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3m m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chung, gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb 0.5kg-1kg\/tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nhanh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nhanh h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho b\u1ea1n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh (\u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng) v\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1, v\u00ec c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 dao \u0111\u1ed9ng trong ng\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c trong tu\u1ea7n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3y t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, s\u0103n ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4828\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4828\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4828 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/an-cham.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/an-cham.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/an-cham-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/an-cham-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/an-cham-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/an-cham-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4828\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f3i quen t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau hao n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m. Vi\u1ec7c c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo n\u1ea1p v\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n ki\u00eang h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u1ee3i. T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m theo, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n rau v\u00e0o b\u1eefa \u0103n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i soda th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng soda \u0103n ki\u00eang. \u0102n nhi\u1ec1u protein, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y v\u00e0 rau gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a The New Gym l\u00e0 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho b\u1eefa \u0103n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc h\u01a1n, ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ea7n \u0103n v\u00e0 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1eefa \u0103n thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1eefa \u0103n thay th\u1ebf l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4793\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4793\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4793 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4793\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n trong v\u00f2ng 6 tu\u1ea7n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong 1 tu\u1ea7n, The New Gym khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n n\u00ean:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp: <\/strong>C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5470\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5470\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5470 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5470\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa t\u1eadp Cardio v\u00e0 t\u1eadp kh\u00e1ng l\u1ef1c:<\/strong> V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau hao n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n khi\u1ebfn cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4910\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4910\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4910 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/khong-bam-vao-tay-vin-hoac-bang-dieu-khien.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/khong-bam-vao-tay-vin-hoac-bang-dieu-khien.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/khong-bam-vao-tay-vin-hoac-bang-dieu-khien-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/khong-bam-vao-tay-vin-hoac-bang-dieu-khien-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/khong-bam-vao-tay-vin-hoac-bang-dieu-khien-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/khong-bam-vao-tay-vin-hoac-bang-dieu-khien-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4910\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa t\u1eadp Cardio v\u00e0 t\u1eadp kh\u00e1ng l\u1ef1c<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u0110\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng 30 &#8211; 90 ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y: <\/strong>\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec trong c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh, ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: thay v\u00ec \u0111i thang m\u00e1y, h\u00e3y \u0111i c\u1ea7u thang b\u1ed9. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo h\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1edbp trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1 &#8211; h\u00e3y t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng theo s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi n\u00f3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5472\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5472\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5472 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym2.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym2.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym2-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym2-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym2-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thenewgym2-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5472\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng 30 &#8211; 90 ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n thay v\u00ec tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o:<\/strong> \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed7i khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y trong 30 ph\u00fat v\u00e0o Th\u1ee9 Ba, th\u00ec v\u00e0o Th\u1ee9 Ba tu\u1ea7n sau, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ea1y trong 32 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y trong 30 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nhanh h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c cao h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 3 hi\u1ec7p 8 l\u1ea7n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean thanh t\u1ea1, th\u00ec sau v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 3 hi\u1ec7p 10 l\u1ea7n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n khi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4894\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4894\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4894 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/nhin-xuong-thay-vi-nhin-phia-truoc-2.png\" alt=\"k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/nhin-xuong-thay-vi-nhin-phia-truoc-2.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/nhin-xuong-thay-vi-nhin-phia-truoc-2-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/nhin-xuong-thay-vi-nhin-phia-truoc-2-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/nhin-xuong-thay-vi-nhin-phia-truoc-2-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/nhin-xuong-thay-vi-nhin-phia-truoc-2-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4894\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n thay v\u00ec tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1